OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain, locally heavy,
OL,6,Fwill be moving eastwards across all
OL,7,Fparts during the morning. Becoming
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter into the afternoon,
OL,9,Falthough a few showers are likely.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith some occasional breaks and the
OL,14,Fchance of showers. Breezy winds
OL,15,Fespecially along the coast.
OL,16,FTemperatures remaining mild overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
