OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with showers,
OL,6,Fthese will ease during the afternoon
OL,7,Fwith some longer sunny spells. The
OL,8,Fwinds will ease during the evening and
OL,9,Fthe cloud will break up.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDrier
OL,12,Fand sunnier with winds easing Sunday.
OL,13,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,14,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,15,FTuesday will be cloudy with coastal
OL,16,Fshowers.
